//Background image, repeat and position can be clubbed into 1:

background: #c21bb1 url(../image/bird.png) left top no-repeat;#c21bb1 url(../image/bird.png) center center no-repeat;


Gradient background: Smooth transition between two colors:
---------------------
background-color:#efh //This is for old browsers
background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, #efh, #FFF) //LAst one is what color do you want to fade to. //to bottom right

CSS sprites: All images are stored in a single file. [use gimp.org or photoshop]
